The spirit can displace the smell.
I'll have some snacks.
If you avoid getting the Rakfisk near your nose, it's not bad - like sushi, which has a rather long bus ride behind you.
Rakfisk is the product of a very different, much poorer Norwegian era, when there were no cooling possibilities yet and fish was soaked in airtight salt water barrels in autumn.
